  SCIENCE FACTS
============================================================

Domain:  Astronomy
Topic:   Hubble's Law
Formula: v = H₀ × d
Note:    Universe is expanding; galaxies recede from us

Domain:  Geology
Topic:   Plate Tectonics
Formula: ~15 major plates on mantle
Note:    Explains earthquakes, volcanoes, mountain formation

Domain:  Astronomy
Topic:   Schwarzschild Radius
Formula: r_s = 2GM/c²
Note:    Event horizon radius of a black hole

Domain:  Biology
Topic:   Photosynthesis
Formula: 6CO₂+6H₂O+light→C₆H₁₂O₆+6O₂
Note:    How plants produce energy from sunlight

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Ohm's Law
Formula: V = IR
Note:    Voltage, current, resistance relationship in circuits

